you to create a mobile account

00:50:57.760 --> 00:51:01.160
and its variations of portable
home directory and an external

00:51:01.160 --> 00:51:03.190
call right from the command line.

00:51:04.260 --> 00:51:09.750
Most interesting parameters are the
-h home path and under -h you can

00:51:09.750 --> 00:51:13.470
actually specify any path to the home,
which means that you're not limited

00:51:13.470 --> 00:51:17.260
to creating the home under /users or
you can create it wherever you want.

00:51:17.440 --> 00:51:19.200
